
Shuppet	 A ghost type Pokémon

SHUPPET is attracted by feelings of 
jealousy and vindictiveness.  If someone 
develops strong feelings of vengeance, 
this POKéMON will appear in a swarm and 
line up beneath the eaves of that person’s 
home. 

